{"tid":302163,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[人體實驗][零準備]唔食得辣反kpop男子獨遊泡菜國十日","createTime":"2017-06-29T07:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T04:29:42.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"361ade2d92f9ddbf7a4ebdaa8e8483f98acf5315","tid":302163,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"。引子<br />\n三月嘅時候睇咗拜恩斯絲打嘅1500蚊七日挑戰post(由佢出完台灣post就深潛，情況令人擔憂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n咁啱嗰陣新識咗個朋友喺首爾讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講講下就趁UO 78蚊買咗飛仁川，<br />\n但因為搶遲咗嘅關係，<br />\n一係淨係去四日，一係去十日(晚機到早機走所以即係自動減兩日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n就心諗反正呢個國家我呢世都唔會再嚟(好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n所以就把心一橫，買咗10日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然係10日咁長，<br />\n但其實我本身又唔中意泡菜，更加唔食得辣，<br />\n更甚嘅係我係No.1反kpop fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n加上我係正常嘅雄性人類，既唔好濕平更唔會整容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想計下自己會用幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我冇拜絲啲budget咁limited <br />\n但我都希望自己唔過2500<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留返啲錢下年返我第二個家鄉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢個唔太算係直播遊記post（唔想用太多電話）<br />\n但我都希望盡量即時上報洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即使唔係每晚都一定會做個統計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望可以控制到自己洗費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有閒都可以分享下見聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一次出呢類post請多多指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4968ccb3d469d5a2665a2e1368328f67d4a2f9","tid":302163,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:38:09.000Z","msg":"屌喇星又搵唔返個post"},{"pid":"67492468f9115089197621f882323853dc3ae785","tid":302163,"uid":5846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T07:41:36.000Z","msg":"十卜，上個月去完泡國，其實好多野都唔辣架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以試下陳玉華一隻雞，上次我地無試到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"954f5c683314d733e2d9d818ab4ef94df6ec8bf3","tid":302163,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"唔食辣都有野好食<br />\n土族村人參雞湯同海鮮餅都好食<br />\n一個人會食唔曬 整飲湯已經夠<br />\n魚串超好味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n烤肉 豬肉特別好食<br />\n可以試下去唔同cafe坐下都幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c972da0c11a1d10c164e4f7b1d3fdb7eef7334fd","tid":302163,"uid":8697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T11:04:18.000Z","msg":"一隻雞 雪濃湯 燒肉 得閒去下cafe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75ac880dae09ff06f7ce35b183e692ca9ad4338","tid":302163,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:32:08.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家 我寧願返大陸都唔撚想去垃圾泡菜國食垃圾泡菜野望垃圾泡菜人"},{"pid":"4f82a694164a66555c6a289f0cba60ae3df09151","tid":302163,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:43:52.000Z","msg":"又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d39b0bb161dae127d0239b53c6d64c15e30de92","tid":302163,"uid":58522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:48:51.000Z","msg":"孔陵 弘大豬腳 廣藏拌飯麻藥手卷都好好食 又唔辣<br />\n去馬場洞食靚牛 阿峴食醬油蟹 仲有炸醬麵 無得輸<br />\n韓國唔係淨係得泡菜同辣"},{"pid":"7c4d530c378ee48436df650cc7d8920f6ecdeb36","tid":302163,"uid":58522,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T03:51:15.000Z","msg":"加多個麻浦水市場食海鮮  <br />\n雖然 係無日本咁多野食同正<br />\n但未到沙漠囉 唔好未試過哂就盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc4fb382075d349badfa0dca93a8069f189f4ac","tid":302163,"uid":1377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢連爛尾都稱唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a1003f1c99634aa7ec77d117053e00df285db2","tid":302163,"uid":44814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加多個麻浦水市場食海鮮  <br />\n雖然 係無日本咁多野食同正<br />\n但未到沙漠囉 唔好未試過哂就盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔係盲反 咁多人反韓菜係有原因<br />\n個次去左6日睇下點解啲friend咁撚鍾意去<br />\n同埋睇下有咩野食啦<br />\n嘩 個啲泡菜炒乜炒乜一大兜個啲真係不了<br />\n炸醬麵啲醬好重口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海鮮唔知點解又整得衰過人 一來佢地鍾意食個啲下闌野怪海鮮 二來唔食腥真係頂唔順<br />\n一隻雞同埋燒肉個啲普通囉 又好難整得難食嘅<br />\ncafe反而幾有特色<br />\n總括黎講佢地料理食物啲方法真係好一般"}]}